item.title: Episode 499: Chapter 11, verses 49 - 52
item.description: Bhagavad Gita Ch. 11 “Yoga of the Vision of the Universal Form” Verses 50, 51, & 52 The lecture discusses Arjuna’s request to see Krishna in the form of Vishnu. Instead, Krishna showed him his gentle human form as Vasudeva, son of Vasudev, and why. Feed: https://neilbhatt.podbean.com/feed.xml
